{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be sleek and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #c0392b; /* Dark Red */\n            --secondary-color: #e74c3c; /* Lighter Red */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark background */\n            --accent-color: #bdc3c7; /* Light Gray */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.8), rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x600/1a1a1a/ffffff?text=Cybersecurity+Background')